      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、私のソロ曲を制作することになった……！？\nそんな、いきなり言われても……本当に私でいいの？",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどころか、遅かったくらいさ\n雫の歌唱力の高さは前から評判になっていたからな",
      "startTime": 13.8665958762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それは言い過ぎ……\nだけど、そう言ってもらえるのは素直に嬉しい……",
      "startTime": 20.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "話はこれだけじゃないぞ。ソロ曲のリリースに合わせて\n雫のソロライブも計画しているんだ",
      "startTime": 29.4333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ソロ曲に加えて、ソロライブまで……\n現実とは思えない……もしかして、これは夢……？",
      "startTime": 35.6416727901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nほっぺた、つねってもいい……？",
      "startTime": 40.2666659038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3000,
          "startTime": 42.2999992371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いてててて！",
      "startTime": 42.2999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "夢じゃない……！！\n全部、現実……！",
      "startTime": 46.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いたた……信じてもらえて良かったよ……\nもし、曲やライブで希望があれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 52.5666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "私の希望……じゃあ……作詞と、衣装のデザイン……\nあと、ライブの演出もやってみたい……",
      "startTime": 62.1666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "凄いやる気だな。だが、今でも毎日忙しいのに\nそこまでやるのは雫の負担が大き過ぎないか？",
      "startTime": 70.200000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "大変なのは分かってる……\nでも、どうしてもやりたい……",
      "startTime": 76.0666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "私には尊敬してるアイドルがいる……\n私はその人の歌とライブから、沢山元気をもらった……",
      "startTime": 82.600000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "もう引退したけど、今でもずっと憧れてる……\n私の永遠の推しアイドル……",
      "startTime": 91.6666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "その人は、作詞作曲はもちろん、ステージの演出まで\n全部自分達でやってた……",
      "startTime": 99.5666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "希望が叶うなら、私も同じようにやってみたい……\n自分の気持ちを歌にして、自分でライブを演出したい",
      "startTime": 106.3333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "初めてのソロ曲とソロライブは……\n私が作り上げる……私の想いを込めたものにしたい……",
      "startTime": 113.9666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "私が憧れた……大好きな、あのアイドルのように……！",
      "startTime": 118.7333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのアイドルのようになんて、雫らしいな……\n分かった。雫の希望が叶うように掛け合ってみるよ",
      "startTime": 129.1082025134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……！　ファンのみんなに\n喜んでもらえるように、私も全力で頑張る……！",
      "startTime": 135.0031010248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 139.9333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今日の仕事はこれで終わりだが\n雫はこの後、真っ直ぐ帰るのか？",
      "startTime": 144.1666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "うん……寮に戻って、ソロ曲の作詞をする……\n早く歌詞を完成させないと……",
      "startTime": 151.1666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "熱心なのはいいが、もうすぐサニピの握手会もあるんだ\n根を詰め過ぎて体調を崩さないようにな",
      "startTime": 158.6666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……作詞で悩んだ時は\nみんなに相談するようにしてるから……",
      "startTime": 164.9000048321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの意見は参考になる……サニピのみんなや\n瑠依さん……最近は、お姉ちゃんからも話を聞いてる",
      "startTime": 171.3946964761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんって……もしかして、雫の従姉妹で\n元BIG4『Baroque』のリーダー……",
      "startTime": 180.6333340964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんのアドバイスは凄く参考になる……\n歌詞のイメージも、お姉ちゃんと話し合って決めた……",
      "startTime": 187.7000007631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "私が今まで経験したことや、感じたことを\n歌にして伝えられたら……って考えてる……",
      "startTime": 195.8333340964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\n雫が言っていた、大好きな憧れのアイドルって……",
      "startTime": 200.6000007631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "私は自分に自信がなくて、ずっと引きこもってた……\nでも、アイドルが好きで……アイドルが心の支えで……",
      "startTime": 212.2333340964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk021.m4a",
